Say "poop!" You're so vulgar, Kageyama-kun!

8
00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:24.810
Crap.

9
00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:26.480
I don't think he actually 
went to the bathroom...

10
00:00:24.810 --> 00:00:25.660
Poop.

11
00:00:25.660 --> 00:00:26.480
Crap.

12
00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:27.370
Poop.

13
00:00:27.370 --> 00:00:27.950
Crap.

14
00:00:27.950 --> 00:00:28.710
Poop!

15
